WEBVTT

NOTE Link at Stonehenge; Attenborough in jungle pursuing walking tree.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
<v Linkman>
This is Stonehenge … and it's from here we go to Africa.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
[action] Jeremy Thorpe appears at edge of shot and waves.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
[action] Jungle location. A large tree foreground. Attenborough pushes through, sweating; two African guides with saxophones.

